<collectingRegion id="49C0F80EFFF8F6168A443F86FAA9F42C" box="[858,1292,2970,2999]" country="Papua New Guinea" name="Southern Highlands" pageId="60" pageNumber="118">Southern Highlands Province</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F313767CFFF8F6168C3C3F86FAC0F42C" box="[1314,1381,2970,2999]" name="Papua New Guinea" pageId="60" pageNumber="118">PNG</collectingCountry>
[= 
<collectingCountry id="F313767CFFF8F6168A263FDEFBEAF444" box="[824,1103,3010,3039]" name="Papua New Guinea" pageId="60" pageNumber="118">Papua New Guinea</collectingCountry>
].”
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBB36ECFFF8F6168A0F3FF9FB2CF357" blockId="60.[783,1383,2887,3315]" pageId="60" pageNumber="118">
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFF8F6168A0F3FF9FBB4F39D" authorityName="Irwin" authorityYear="2017" box="[785,1041,3045,3078]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Nyctimene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="118" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="wrightae">Nyctimene wrightae</taxonomicName>
is tentatively included in the 
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFF8F6168A633810FC77F3B6" authorityName="K. Andersen" authorityYear="1910" box="[893,978,3084,3117]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Nyctimene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="118" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="cyclotis">cyclotis</taxonomicName>
species group, although it shares many traits with N. albwenter papuanus. Populations attributed to N. wnrightae have been treated as N. 
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFF8F6168DD4389FFABAF33F" authorityName="K. Andersen" authorityYear="1910" box="[1226,1311,3203,3236]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Nyctimene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="118" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="cyclotis">cyclotis</taxonomicName>
and N. a. papuanus. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
